{"tid":101844,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"microeconomics 一問","createTime":"2017-01-31T07:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T08:52:46.000Z","uid":76616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c737e1d68b4c85e5b990ce26f2ee9f93d4b50b9d","tid":101844,"uid":76616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T07:59:55.000Z","msg":"點解marginal cost 要存在，反映到d咩，同埋佢同ATC有咩關係？"},{"pid":"a5105e7cfebcae6d76fd3c8bc19577c8f0079ee6","tid":101844,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T08:52:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解marginal cost 要存在，反映到d咩，同埋佢同ATC有咩關係？</blockquote><br />\nMarginal cost即係生產額外一件產品，total cost會增加幾多<br />\n<br />\n例如一間餐廳生產10個餐嘅total cost係$200，生產11個嘅total cost係$210<br />\n第11個餐marginal cost就係$10"}]}